{"id":"e1b20cc7c1e15cb16ae414ad870e24cc521aeaf1b089de368e3f65fedffb6226","item_id":"6ca3fae752:0","text":"在 RenderMan for Blender 中进行皮毛和毛发渲染/着色时，可以沿用 Blender 中渲染毛发的常规方式。用于毛发的主要 RenderMan 材质是"}
{"id":"ccf31fc48275c143b867da4b33a4ee3f6d4e505c6b15e85616384686e98b23fe","item_id":"6ca3fae752:1","text":"PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"id":"c076b140fbc670364be197b40bba12bd87f3dd2ceda2e8bf7efe582bd2af4ddd","item_id":"6ca3fae752:3","text":"创建毛发系统"}
{"id":"52df78c0283738556b0499d5d3e33804856f5600be3a2cd91c09b9752ed61926","item_id":"6ca3fae752:4","text":"若要创建毛发系统，请选择要添加毛发的网格对象，然后点击粒子属性"}
{"id":"2af642e3bf799f5837eaa59b63bba3ac986a3b8b6096e74baffb17bc3fc59868","item_id":"6ca3fae752:5","text":"。添加新的粒子系统，并选择 Hair（毛发）。"}
{"id":"f93977db04555b8f708d1e987b06450193b76b58bcebd3514d46aed12d12185d","item_id":"6ca3fae752:6","text":"你的对象在 viewport（视口）中应大致如下。"}
{"id":"a67e15a12874a8f615ed1c27fb85d63306ffbcd8b655bd83c4e01630563ea108","item_id":"6ca3fae752:7","text":"毛发着色"}
{"id":"ab2fe23aaf0bf0ce13f3861191dc3d2304cc7b9a831c5615998fd427ce2c9947","item_id":"6ca3fae752:8","text":"如前所述，我们会使用 PxrMarschnerHair 材质为毛发着色。为此，请点击网格的材质属性"}
{"id":"3b3f00f0be8c1c63d4fdbc8128d6c9d8240c7032fac630b3dbf6a20544dbec29","item_id":"6ca3fae752:9","text":"。在材质列表中，点击 + 按钮添加新的材质插槽，然后点击 New（新建）。"}
{"id":"360cd2b66723b778ef123a2e0804737270fd521f71d70baf30af1092fe106903","item_id":"6ca3fae752:10","text":"点击 Add RenderMan Nodetree（添加 RenderMan 节点树），然后从下拉菜单中选择 PxrMarschnerHair。"}
{"id":"a8bf3c799e097954e55c5123d8014b51a13f396838a24ae6f516fa139e4c4cac","item_id":"6ca3fae752:11","text":"回到粒子属性"}
{"id":"2b08ae6a93a47b073f1efab0034279d2b93507031564d17d660b97397613379e","item_id":"6ca3fae752:12","text":"中，进入 Render（渲染）部分，并将 Material（材质）改为我们刚添加的 PxrMarschnerHair 新材质。"}
{"id":"3e63b5b47bfa25f46493ea6d010432dbffdd82672ccbe45dc0d7ff6cd25a88f8","item_id":"6ca3fae752:13","text":"Artistic Control（艺术控制）"}
{"id":"c70354ed721825bafb24790f22fda028bbf199759d69055271cfde3533e9cb6f","item_id":"6ca3fae752:14","text":"PxrMarschnerHair 材质应该足以渲染真实感毛发。不过，这些参数可能有点偏技术化。为了获得更适合艺术家的控制，可以在 PxrMarschnerHair 之外配合使用 PxrHairColor pattern 节点。PxrHairColor 有三个输出需要连接到 PxrMarschnerHair。最好使用 Shader Editor（着色器编辑器）"}
{"id":"995d5837c8233cbeb7cd66fcc66769917ce7e5b3ec54b13beeb5872de1f60754","item_id":"6ca3fae752:15","text":"来完成这些连接。下图展示了它们应如何连接。"}
{"id":"cf55fbb6ec5bf2cfaa728a0b41d9f8c2e6bd2abdca406d7825c44da27c2b9439","item_id":"6ca3fae752:16","text":"将 Mode（模式）改为 Artistic（艺术化）后，可以获得更适合艺术家的控制，帮助完成毛发着色。"}
{"id":"69eaa33622cbb95b830f3b82750d7ac2832dcf06e96f7358fbc708064797f981","item_id":"6ca3fae752:17","text":"Hair ID Primvar（毛发 ID Primvar）"}
{"id":"363def04ba0396a6ad1ac0db107f9e47ce627a83d45655c1b4f7a12a8097897f","item_id":"6ca3fae752:18","text":"PxrHairColor 包含用于为颜色添加随机性的控制项。这由一个 ID primitive variable 控制。在 RenderMan for Blender 中，我们会为每一根毛发添加一个 \"index\" primitive variable。这个 \"index\" primitive variable 可作为 ID primvar 的来源。"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "6ca3fae752:2", "text": "。"}
